sequenceDiagram
    title EduAdapt
    actor Student
    participant System as EduAdapt System

    Student->>System: Login
    System-->>Student: Display Dashboard
    Student->>System: Select Course
    Student->>System: Engage with Content
    Student->>System: Submit Quiz

    alt Score < 60
        System-->>Student: Suggest: 'Review Material'
    else 60 <= Score < 85
        System-->>Student: Unlock next module (Same Level)
    else Score >= 85
        System-->>Student: Unlock next module, 'Level Up' & Award Badge
    end